    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "葵、『情熱だけで生きてみろ』の\nMVの撮影日程、メールで送ったけど確認したか？",
      "startTime": 3.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "確認してあるよ\nそれにしても、初披露からだいぶ時間が空いたね",
      "startTime": 9.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "『Grab the BIG4』で曲を披露したのは\n随分前だよ。もっと早くやれば良かったのに",
      "startTime": 15.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "あの曲はいつリリースするの、って\n会う人みんなに言われて困ってるんだけどな",
      "startTime": 22.666666158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そもそも『Grab the BIG4』で\nあの曲を披露する予定はなかったからな",
      "startTime": 28.266666158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "そうだっけ。んー、そうだったかもね",
      "startTime": 31.2999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "だからMV撮影の準備なんてしてなかったんだよ\nそれにBIG4になってすぐ、海外ツアーに行っただろ",
      "startTime": 38.9999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "レコーディングだって、ついこの間済ませたばかりだ\nむしろ早かったと思ってほしいくらいだよ",
      "startTime": 46.5333328247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "そっか。{user}君は、最速で撮影を\n組んでくれたんだね。じゃあ、ありがとう",
      "startTime": 53.766666158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ苦労はしたが、それが俺の仕事だからな\nところで、俺からも一つ、質問をいいか？",
      "startTime": 62.0333328247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "何が聞きたいの？　僕が今ハマってる音ゲーとか？\n一つならいいよ。僕の質問に一つ答えてもらったからね",
      "startTime": 65.6999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "もっと大事なことだよ。その例の曲についてなんだが\n活動休止中に、葵が振り付けを作っていたよな",
      "startTime": 80.0333328247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、状況的に四人で合わせる時間なんてなかった\nどうして準決勝で、あんなに完璧に合わせられたんだ？",
      "startTime": 88.2999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "いや……そもそもあの勝負所で、どうして満足に\n練習も出来ていない、未発表の新曲をやったんだ？",
      "startTime": 96.3999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、あの時も同じようなことを聞かれたっけ\nというか、質問が二つある気がするんだけど",
      "startTime": 104.6013351094,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "もしもインタビューなんかで急に話されでもしたら\n困るからな。さすがに把握しておきたいんだ",
      "startTime": 111.4333328247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4になった直後は、慌ただしかったから\nなぁなぁにされたけど……今度こそ、話してもらうぞ？",
      "startTime": 117.7333328247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "分かったよ。大した話じゃないけど\nそんなに知りたいなら話すよ",
      "startTime": 126.4333328247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "あれは、『Grab the BIG4』\n決勝トーナメント開始の、少し前の話なんだけど――",
      "startTime": 130.9999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_corridor_evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "ここで曲調が変わるから、フォーメーションも変えて\n……少し難しいステップだけど、みんななら出来るはず",
      "startTime": 141.4999954224,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7633.333333299987,
          "startTime": 144.3999954224
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様、葵\n……もしかして、新曲の振り付けを作ってるのか？",
      "startTime": 148.9999954224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "うん。活動休止中とはいえ\n僕も一応まだ、リズノワのメンバーだからね",
      "startTime": 155.7333287557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "自分でやるって言い出したことなんだから、やらないと\nそれで{user}君は何しに来たの？",
      "startTime": 163.3999954224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "葵がリズノワの活動をしばらく休むって聞いたから\n心配して、様子を見に来たんだ",
      "startTime": 169.9999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "そう。面倒見がいいね、{user}君は\nでも、僕のことは気にしないで",
      "startTime": 177.2333287557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワにとって大切な時に、こんな所にいる僕に\n時間をかける必要なんてない。それより……",
      "startTime": 184.4333287557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "『Grab the BIG4』の決勝トーナメントを\n控えてる、莉央達のそばにいてあげてほしい",
      "startTime": 190.7333287557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん達のこと、気にかけてるんだな\n大丈夫。三人のフォローはしっかりやるから任せてくれ",
      "startTime": 197.8666620891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "でも、葵にだって助けは必要だ。莉央さん達と\n距離を取っている今の葵には、相談相手がいた方がいい",
      "startTime": 206.6666620891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi016.m4a",
      "text": "僕に助けが……相談相手が必要？\nそう、なのかな",
      "startTime": 215.9666620891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "俺はそう思ってる。今は相談ごとがないならそれでいい\nもし何か話したいことが出来たら、声を掛けてくれ",
      "startTime": 223.1666620891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
